"""
parameter_tuner.py — Dynamic Hyperparameter Tuning & Evolutionary Optimization Engine

Implements:
  - Dynamic learning rate annealing curves (cosine warm-restart, exponential decay, step-decay)
  - Hyperparameter configuration matrices with bounded search spaces
